{"tid":305554,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"借唔借相機俾兄弟去旅行用","createTime":"2017-07-01T18:04:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-02T08:53:10.000Z","uid":124686,"like":4,"dislike":131,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2e2fa7be1b7a8489a0d2659fb577c8e97bd9743a","tid":305554,"uid":124686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T18:04:28.000Z","msg":"我細佬諗住去歐洲，無啦啦問我借部機去影下相，但佢又唔係本身影相個啲人。又話會鍚住又話跌爛左賠返黎。<br />\n其實佢個人本身唔算好錫機既人，有時又好論盡個啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但見佢去歐洲咁開心，又話會影啲靚相黎。<br />\n借唔借俾佢好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d0af9d8682af9669f6bac7d6369e1c48466d61b","tid":305554,"uid":124686,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T18:06:28.000Z","msg":"80D，加上唔係啲咩貴鏡。<br />\n但我都好唔放借比佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4388d538d4065e8ceddcf3bd88903f77834bc03c","tid":305554,"uid":237,"like":8,"dislike":46,"score":-38,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T18:08:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>80D，加上唔係啲咩貴鏡。<br />\n但我都好唔放借比佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n最憎d人咁縮骨小家"},{"pid":"3247ac00f1695de3be66f543b372e7e691902a67","tid":305554,"uid":57359,"like":66,"dislike":0,"score":66,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T18:10:34.000Z","msg":"你細佬都話左有咩事會賠翻比你啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />朋友都算啦，仲要兩兄弟，成件事根本你都無損失，唔明點解你仲要考慮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a5ff4afca007142f29e4366e85a84886e672def","tid":305554,"uid":68081,"like":67,"dislike":0,"score":67,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T18:15:20.000Z","msg":"屋企人多多都借，完"},{"pid":"39a7806ac1916395cca29882b8393566d64be3e5","tid":305554,"uid":54181,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T18:16:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fd788cf97978dea763a54d805a1fb3cae298f000","tid":305554,"uid":11448,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T18:17:46.000Z","msg":"80d就算啦 無想像中咁易壞（如果正正經經咁影）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1eef98f3bb75dfeae72b93f0f814be5a248faaee","tid":305554,"uid":64714,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T18:22:57.000Z","msg":"同你一樣情況 我細佬連光圈快門ISO都唔識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最後都係借左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n難得去旅行 無謂掃佢興"},{"pid":"4e624b900f46a272611d19565a4e47a6022fd0e1","tid":305554,"uid":73443,"like":30,"dislike":0,"score":30,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T18:23:22.000Z","msg":"你睇你喇<br />\n我借完比阿哥去之前又話爛左送過部比我<br />\n又話好小心又咩<br />\n之後返黎同我講部野訓訓覺既時候自己爆左個mon<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不如話去旅行遇到黑衣人 部野幫佢擋左下一陽指好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後話佢負責整返好(發9我老皮)<br />\n結果到最後佢自己買過部但我個部連屍都唔知去左邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d36a1e8719b956284804ac23271680fcaf4169b","tid":305554,"uid":9907,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T18:26:22.000Z","msg":"屋企人都唔借<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"596a483c16e7156787bc2b2c2e3d6eb309f63dd6","tid":305554,"uid":20390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T18:28:24.000Z","msg":"其實去旅行唔買保險？"},{"pid":"052bab765c1c89765ccb6251ee94fbc1c6009ca9","tid":305554,"uid":124686,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T18:33:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>80D，加上唔係啲咩貴鏡。<br />\n但我都好唔放借比佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n最憎d人咁縮骨小家</blockquote><br />\n巴打鬧得啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都認我自私，自己兄弟就唔好咁縮骨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但巴打有無咩例子係好瀟灑咁借野比人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 因為我都有我立場，部相機係出黎做野買比自己既禮物，我唔係話佢一定會整壞或者係佢整壞會唔賠，但點做到咁瀟灑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5b37ddbc942e9f7824dbe8b4b81ba33823e78fe","tid":305554,"uid":34209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T18:35:30.000Z","msg":"都識講自己兄弟啦 <br />\n自己兄弟 佢先問你借"},{"pid":"3c4d9b5d6783bbde67d78cbdb88a203c5a7e4838","tid":305554,"uid":94418,"like":44,"dislike":4,"score":40,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T18:35:34.000Z","msg":"男人三不借：車，相機，老婆"},{"pid":"bace11e729b3ea5eda37ce20c6f304e08b5ee8b6","tid":305554,"uid":124686,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T18:35:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屋企人都唔借<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n借我一定借，但做唔到巴打咁瀟灑啫"},{"pid":"03b59fa051b9010436cd01697da9354e9b113b76","tid":305554,"uid":54861,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T18:37:17.000Z","msg":"借。緊係借蹬。<br />\n朋友就話say no姐<br />\n自己兄弟姊妹一定借。<br />\n<br />\n最多，如果整爛左，咪狠狠地diu 9佢囉。<br />\n<br />\n不過你口吻似唔想借，又話咩禮物又成，<br />\n搵晒藉口咁，你心入面有晒答案。<br />\n咁都仲要問？<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95dcbc2472f5fc691c936c9e7992d94ffb26b642","tid":305554,"uid":124686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T18:37:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>男人三不借：車，相機，老婆</blockquote><br />\n老婆唯一不借，其他睇人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f55cf042abd79aa7790066fdb542f3afea92f870","tid":305554,"uid":31173,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T18:41:26.000Z","msg":"咁撚度縮就咪撚借啦，陣間借完日日諗住就無撚謂啦"},{"pid":"18b72f69f396f8a1db76dc31538b577e768410b1","tid":305554,"uid":124686,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T18:51:12.000Z","msg":"<blockq