就唔好啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"976e59c8e5ec89f6ac45ab9bb00d6f549bab6302","tid":305554,"uid":8268,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T19:39:14.000Z","msg":"我都係80d。我家姐去日本玩，佢未用過單反我都借畀佢用"},{"pid":"159af13a3cb12275e743c98090b49a8aec51a1a5","tid":305554,"uid":13958,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T19:55:32.000Z","msg":"樓主咁唔願意借就唔好勉強<br />\n一係你問佢拎住幾千蚊黎做押金先<br />\n我覺得兩兄弟<br />\n既然佢講得話爛左會賠<br />\n佢就唔應該介意比左呢筆錢先"},{"pid":"228d1522de8a1a92c94340cf9f2a39e0f1d52bed","tid":305554,"uid":35021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T19:55:37.000Z","msg":"相機睇邊啲啦，<br />\n我就同一個系統買多部二手入門，<br />\n借比屋企人用，<br />\n鏡就比枝平kit用，<br />\n家人除非真喺用嘢用得太粗，<br />\n唔喺的話盡量會借"},{"pid":"35562fcc2bbbe90f9482e3865b8af7e8cd8db1ba","tid":305554,"uid":25699,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T20:02:27.000Z","msg":"街外人唔借<br />\n親兄弟咪借比佢囉<br />\n就算爛咗唔通佢走你數咩"},{"pid":"80a6cfad9da702bf9b309b3a24f6918d4f66e3b1","tid":305554,"uid":13358,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T20:03:14.000Z","msg":"好彩冇兄弟<br />\n最憎借野比人"},{"pid":"150849aae78559d98ca1f79facaa79b4cb3ff524","tid":305554,"uid":3068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T22:33:16.000Z","msg":"買份旅遊保險囉！試過都賠得足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申：非保險狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0209f2eb36957e10db7c2cb7bc6e7e26540eb00e","tid":305554,"uid":117044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T22:36:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"68ad1bfc009301df18aa69506c5c06fabffaf79a","tid":305554,"uid":41924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-01T22:51:01.000Z","msg":"你同你細佬關係好差咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁都咁計較<br />\n又唔係唔還俾你"},{"pid":"8ea4a33cd721611b014cfda2af115e502a2ad180",